## Maintenance Notes

- Always `docker compose` on CasaOS, never `docker-compose`
- GPU passthrough: check vendor-reset if VM won't start after host reboot
- Ollama must bind to `0.0.0.0:11434` — not just localhost
- WireGuard tunnel health: `ping 192.168.50.19` from VPS — if it fails, check OPNsense WireGuard status
- Certbot auto-renews — if a cert is stale, `certbot renew --dry-run` on VPS to test
